      {"speaker": "范一平", "chinese": "你们的价格也是最贵的吧?", "pinyin": "Nǐmen de jiàgé ye shi zuì guì de ba?", "english": "Your prices are the most expensive, right?"},
      {"speaker": "服务员", "chinese": "我们一共有十四艘豪华旅游船,船上的条件非常好。", "pinyin": "Wǒmen yìgòng yǒu shísì sōu háohuá lǚyóu chuán, chuánshang de tiáojiàn fēicháng háo.", "english": "We have 14 luxury cruise ships, the conditions on board are excellent."},
      {"speaker": "服务员", "chinese": "可以说跟五星级宾馆没有两样。", "pinyin": "Kěyǐ shuō gēn wǔ xīngjí bīnguǎn méiyǒu liǎngyàng.", "english": "You could say it's no different from a five-star hotel."},
      {"speaker": "范一平", "chinese": "听起来确实不错,可惜我没有那么多钱。", "pinyin": "Tīngqǐlai quèshi búcuò, kěxī wǒ méiyǒu nàme duō qián.", "english": "Sounds really nice, but I don't have that much money unfortunately."}
